---
title: Quick American Crumbed Chicken with Roast Pumpkin & Apple Slaw
description:  A golden crumb on juicy chicken is like a bond between star-crossed lovers - unbeatable. Our All-American spice blend brings smokey and savoury flavours to this crunchy coating, perfectly complemented by the sweetness of roast pumpkin and apple in the slaw.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
